ming's \\\"race\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"the century\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Already one of the greatest swimmers ever and a multiple world record holder throughout her career, Ledecky will head to Paris looking to add to her six individual Olympic gold medals.\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.443730819617003e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the greatest swimmers\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"a multiple world record holder\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"her six individual Olympic gold medals\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old qualified in the 200-metre, 400-metre, 800-metre and 1,500-metre freestyle - although she expects to drop the individual 200-metre to focus on the 800-metre and 1,500-metre free, considered her best shots at victory.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 200-metre, 400-metre\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"800-metre\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"1,500-metre freestyle\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual 200-metre\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800-metre\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"1,500-metre free\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"her best shots\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 915}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky is aiming for a fourth straight 800-metre free gold and another 1,500-metre crown.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"a fourth straight 800-metre free gold\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"another 1,500-metre crown\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's in the blue-ribband 400-metre freestyle event where three of the greatest swimmers of the modern era will collide.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the blue-ribband 400-metre freestyle event\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest swimmers\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern era\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky, the 2016 400-metre Olympic champion, faces stiff competition from Australia's Ariarne Titmus, who stunned the American in the 400-metre freestyle at the 2020 Tokyo Olympics and currently owns the world record.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8976847068856036, \"rank\": 0.11088752003044869, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}, {\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9986793895965106, \"rank\": 0.0010514228432337081, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 400-metre Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1178}, {\"ngram\": \"stiff competition\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400-metre freestyle\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both Ledecky and Titmus will also have to be wary of sensational Canadian teenager Summer McIntosh, who also held the 400-metre world record until early 2023, when Titmus snatched it back at the 2023 world championships.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1371, \"end\": 1377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}, {\"begin\": 1419, \"end\": 1427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9998370164558765, \"rank\": 0.00016301011073038542, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 1437, \"end\": 1452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Summer McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\"}, {\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbped