\": \"superstardom\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"87.58 metres\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023, the 26-year-old also became the first Indian to win a gold medal at the World Athletics Championships, when he pipped Nadeem with an 88.17-metre effort in the final.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2303, \"end\": 2309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999478541226, \"rank\": 5.2142859164222355e-08, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2337, \"end\": 2366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999999949964149, \"rank\": 4.646370713388807e-09, \"text\": \"World Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"an 88.17-metre effort\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chopra's personal best throw is 89.94 metres, which he recorded at the Stockholm Diamond League in 2022.\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2513, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.370676423082183e-35, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chopra's personal best throw\", \"from