 to go for gold.\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3190}, {\"ngram\": \"his best chance\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3210}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years after a positive marijuana test saw her kicked off the US team for the Tokyo Olympics, Sha'Carri Richardson has earned a chance for Olympic redemption.\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3295, \"end\": 3297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3171379688675136e-15, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3327, \"end\": 3347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sha'Carri Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sha'Carri_Richardson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a positive marijuana test\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3271}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3325}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3367}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic redemption\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson will be the one to beat in Paris as she arrives in the French capital following her gold medal triumph in the World Athletics Championships last year in Hungary.\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3393, \"end\": 3403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999991781172606, \"rank\": 8.208764586147975e-07, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215